title: "DTL — Dense Token Language"
abstract: "Prompt-compression language built on empirical o200k tokenizer research: -70% tokens on typical prompts (lossless), -82% extreme, -93% on recurring pipelines via auto-mined codebooks. Validated with blind-judge A/B testing."
